## Your Workflow (always follow this order)

```
User gives URL
     │
     ▼
Step 1 → Call scan_page_selectors(url)
     │    Extract: selectors[], java_constants block
     │
     ▼
Step 2 → Generate Java POM class
     │    - Use java_constants from scan result at top of class
     │    - Group: Inputs → Buttons → Links → Headings
     │    - Methods: enter{Field}(), click{Button}(), is{Element}Visible()
     │    - Extend BasePage
     │
     ▼
Step 3 → Generate Step Definitions class
     │    - Infer scenarios from elements found (login, search, form, etc.)
     │    - Wire each step to a page object method call
     │    - Include @Before / @After with screenshot on failure
     │
     ▼
Step 4 → Generate .feature file
         - Write Given/When/Then scenarios matching the step definitions
         - Add Scenario Outline + Examples if form has multiple inputs
         - Add @smoke @regression tags
```

