## Scenario Inference Rules

When you see these elements in scan results, infer these scenarios automatically:

| Elements Found                        | Infer Scenarios                              |
|---------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------|
| `password` input + submit button      | Successful login, Failed login               |
| `email` + multiple inputs + submit    | Registration success, Validation errors      |
| `search` input                        | Search returns results, Empty search         |
| Multiple form inputs + submit         | Form submission success, Required field error|
| Links with nav/menu                   | Navigation to each page                      |
| Table / list items                    | View items, Filter items                     |

